{"tid":1578753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記者必須通過「學習強国」APP考試才能申領記者證","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:25:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c443a5905422afc299454ec2621330aa2cac840f","tid":1578753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"中共中宣部稍早前公布新規定，今年將透過「學習強國」手機App，對全國新聞編採人員展開在線崗位培訓考試，記者必須通過包括「習思想」等內容的考試，才能申領新版記者證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/18/2136098-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F18%2F2136098-XXL.jpg&h=8adde9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合新浪網等陸媒報導，中宣部傳媒監管局8月23日發出「關於在『學習強國』學習平台創建和認證新聞採編學習組織的通知」，其中對新聞單位申領新版新聞記者證做出具體要求。<br />\n<br />\n根據通知，申領者須通過「學習強國」平台手機用戶端的培訓考試，通過後才能申領新版記者證。<br />\n<br />\n考試內容包括「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」、「習近平總書記關於宣傳思想工作的重要講話」、馬克思主義新聞觀、新聞倫理與政策法規以及新聞採編業務。<br />\n<br />\n據最新消息，本月底會有一批試點單位進行「試點考試」，而正式考試初定於10月上旬，採閉卷方式；考試不合格的，另行安排考試，只能補考一次。<br />\n<br />\n此外，各新聞單位須在「學習強國」學習平台完成新聞採編學習組織的創建和認證，否則無法參加考試和申領新版新聞記者證。<br />\n<br />\n「學習強國」是由中共中央宣傳部主管、以中共總書記習近平的講話和「習思想」為主要內容的「理論學習平台」，包括網站和手機app，今年1月初上線。<br />\n<br />\n中共當局一度要求9000萬黨員都必須下載「學習強國」app來學習「習思想」，並提出學習積分制，但據香港星島日報先前報導，強制下載的規定已經因為「民怨」而取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=604388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D604388&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=17c41421\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D604388&h=5f886cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=604388</a>"},{"pid":"34c427d321496edd55d8151020c22cd6772e474a","tid":1578753,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a62c8849a0b4630b6ef3f98a51c6c16793c490","tid":1578753,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"習乳綠"},{"pid":"3ac841bfc7abd99d3beee06ba8b9cb6620a05c27","tid":1578753,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"全國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9725ca3770e3cc2edf106d8266986b189836240","tid":1578753,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"笑左 巨嬰國"},{"pid":"9a25b31308e164e33fcf7220af0da4b53980acd6","tid":1578753,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"真係認撚左自己係強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cc835156aaca7a8323b139474ad7866d0954d1","tid":1578753,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"